        <p>If you left-click on tag bars, you can drag them up or down. If you left-click on table column bars (in the span bar area), you can drag them left or right. In this way, the chunks of topic content can easily be repositioned. In addition, you can click on the borders between column and row bars and drag the mouse to resize individual columns and rows. <MadCap:conditionalText MadCap:conditions="Products.Flare-Online-Only">See <MadCap:xref href="../../../../../Flare/Interface/Editors/XML-Editor/Structure-Bars/Moving-Paragraphs-Content-Structure-Bars.htm">Moving Paragraphs and Content with Structure Bars</MadCap:xref>, <MadCap:xref href="../../../../../Flare/Interface/Editors/XML-Editor/Structure-Bars/Moving-Table-Columns-Rows1.htm">Moving Table Columns and Rows</MadCap:xref>, and <MadCap:xref href="../../../../../Flare/Tables/Main-Activities/Resizing-Tables.htm">Resizing Tables</MadCap:xref>.</MadCap:conditionalText><MadCap:conditionalText MadCap:conditions="Products.Contributor">See <MadCap:xref href="../../../../../Contributor/Editor-Tools/Structure-Bars/Moving-Paragraphs-Content-Structure-Bars.htm">Moving Paragraphs and Other Content with Structure Bars</MadCap:xref>, <MadCap:xref href="../../../../../Contributor/Tables/Moving-Table-Columns-Rows.htm">Moving Table Columns and Rows</MadCap:xref>, and <MadCap:xref href="../../../../../Contributor/Tables/Resizing-Tables.htm">Resizing Tables</MadCap:xref>.</MadCap:conditionalText></p>
